displayName: Entrance to the Great Tumble Marsh

parameters:
Thief Nora: Are you okay?! Sophia-san, can I ask for your
help?
Cleric Sophia: Yes, please leave it to me.

Thief Emma: I'm really grateful... being chased by the
Imperial Army... I've been cornered this far.

Thief Emma: I think the captain's unit is safe, but I
believe it's only a matter of time before the total assault
on the hideout begins.
Thief Nora: There are still injured people ahead, right?

Thief Emma: There are injured people besides me, so please
be careful if you go inside.

Thief Emma: There's a giant snake lurking around. We won't
be able to pass through the marshland unless we defeat it.

Thief Nora: Please leave this place first. I will
definitely rescue everyone!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
